W wywiadzie czytamy m.in.: "Przykładamy dużą uwagę do tego, w jakim systemie pracują nasi ludzie. Pracownicy też powinni wiedzieć, jak funk­cjonuje firma, w jaki sposób jest zarządzana oraz wspólnie wyznaczać kolejne etapy rozwoju. To jest coś, co chcieliśmy stworzyć od samego początku."

Całość wywiadu można przeczytać w ostatnim wydaniu magazynu <a href="https://mdc2.pl/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/eurologistics_2022_03_01_przejrzystosa_i_dynamiczny_rozwoj_pdf_bn_k_p.pdf">Eurologistics.</a>

&nbsp;

"We pay a lot of attention to the structure in which our people work. Employees should also know how the company works, how it is managed and together determine the next stages of its growth. This is something we wanted to create. from the beginning." - said Maciej Madejak.

You can read the entire interview (available in Polish)  in the latest issue of <a href="https://mdc2.pl/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/eurologistics_2022_03_01_przejrzystosa_i_dynamiczny_rozwoj_pdf_bn_k_p.pdf">Eurologistics.</a>

&nbsp;

It was an honour to be awarded in two out of three Popular Choice categories during the recent <a href="https://eurobuildcee.com/en/post/32839-the-glorious-twelfth">Eurobuild CEE Awards</a>: <strong>Newcomer of the Year and Outstanding Non-Business Achievement of the Year</strong> which recognized our charity association, <a href="https://ukrainerelief.pl/">Ukraine Relief </a>helping Polish families hosting Ukrainian refugees in their homes and supporting Ukrainian children who are aiming to settled down in Poland.

The awards were granted to the best the market can offer in 35 categories, in a process that was entrusted to almost 200 judges and independent auditing company KPMG.

Kudos to our team and business partners for everything we achieved in the last 18 months.

